name: Allen Passmore
text: I love this pizza! Great food, great prices and if something is a little off they go out of their way to make it right. Above and beyond! Best pizza in town!

name: lawtonokiedude
text: Subpar pizza at most. Most of the staff were either slacking off or yelling at each other over orders. I've seen some chaotic restaurants in my 20+ years as an executive chef, but this place takes the cake. I would give it zero stars if I could. Save your money and try somewhere else.

name: Trinity Luke
text: Excellent service. Always  helpful and smiling. Thank you.

name: Jean Willliams
text: Excellent customer service as well as the best pizza around !

name: Michael McCurdy
text: Would be better if their online ordering ever worked

name: Cisneros
text: Some of the best tasting pizza in the area.

name: Joshua Yates
text: I think I was the last customer of the night. They delivered my pizza, car side.

name: jeff butler
text: Best pizza and sub in Duncan
